{"tid":1521331,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"荔枝角嘅居民聽住","createTime":"2019-08-31T07:04:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T07:38:12.000Z","uid":172376,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"746f62bc2e1642b19fde8dcba197d5cfe94b3cd1","tid":1521331,"uid":172376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T07:04:12.000Z","msg":"住係荔枝角嘅良好市民：<br />\n無論住四小龍西九龍一號定海麗邨<br />\n我明白到今日係禮拜六<br />\n有好多人都放假而唔會出街<br />\n但經過呢2個幾月再加上呢2日嘅白色恐怖<br />\n我作為一個香港人<br />\n見到自己原有嘅野被人發現一一咁剝奪<br />\n如果大家今日唔企出嚟<br />\n聽日可能連出街同著咩衫嘅自由到無<br />\n~<br />\n我希望大家係4點鐘開始<br />\n一齊落街行下企下/做下運動跑下步<br />\n呼吸下剩低小小自由嘅空氣<br />\n&bull;<br />\n荔枝角嘅市民<br />\n我希望可以係4點見到大家<br />\n#遍地開花"},{"pid":"eac8dc6990dc0d83e5b531097b59b9fb5c61d328","tid":1521331,"uid":172376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T07:04:43.000Z","msg":"4點一齊落街行下"},{"pid":"150e63711848fd3fd9511524922c4cf566a2994f","tid":1521331,"uid":172376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T07:05:04.000Z","msg":"健康人生由我做起"},{"pid":"b72a6b2bfc983aec7db3eaaa15850df9d3c73241","tid":1521331,"uid":172376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T07:05:44.000Z","msg":"唔好再覺得事不關己<br />\n我地係土生土長嘅香港人<br />\n香港嘅事 就係我地嘅事"},{"pid":"78a2c534f21066aeae6074fa14dce8ec3de410bc","tid":1521331,"uid":172376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T07:06:05.000Z","msg":"希望4點唔係得我一個行"},{"pid":"54b250810708b6bee2e4f37fe9e8fb43c68652b1","tid":1521331,"uid":172376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T07:07:00.000Z","msg":"大家要出左嚟先<br />\n啲人住樓上望到無人都唔會落嚟啦"},{"pid":"62ce4081304ebf6aff56fe6dc5b5107e563aace9","tid":1521331,"uid":172376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T07:07:13.000Z","msg":"各區各有各做"},{"pid":"18aed493955575a38c3f7e6027ca61023001be15","tid":1521331,"uid":172376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T07:07:34.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"6e2e8ae27f590d